ViewObject.Name: ProgramView
ViewObject.SQLQuery:
select ID, NAME, CODE, SUBSTANCE, DESCRIPTION, CREATE_DATE, UPDATE_DATE, IS_SYNCING, SYNC_DATE, HAS_INACTIVE_PROJECTS, HAS_PROJECTS, NAME SEARCH_NAME, CODE SEARCH_CODE, is_dev_empty from( SELECT Program.ID, Program.NAME, Program.CODE, Program.SUBSTANCE, Program.DESCRIPTION, Program.CREATE_DATE, Program.UPDATE_DATE, Program.IS_SYNCING, Program.SYNC_DATE, nvl((SELECT 1 FROM Project WHERE Program.Id = Project.Program_Id AND Project.IS_ACTIVE = 0 AND rownum = 1),0) HAS_INACTIVE_PROJECTS, nvl((SELECT 1 FROM Project WHERE Program.Id = Project.Program_Id AND rownum = 1),0) HAS_PROJECTS, Program.NAME SEARCH_NAME, Program.CODE SEARCH_CODE, decode(nvl((SELECT 1 FROM Project WHERE Program.Id = Project.Program_Id and area_code in ('PRE-POT','POST-POT') AND rownum = 1),0),0,1,0) is_dev_empty FROM PROGRAM Program ) pg where ( -- begin Search filter for Dev VC :SearchVcName='Dev' and (pg.is_dev_empty = :SearchProgramIsEmptyVar and pg.is_dev_empty = 1 or exists (select 1 from project pj left join ( select name, code from bay_number ) bn on bn.code = pj.bay_code where pj.program_id=pg.id and (pj.is_hpr=:SearchIsHprVar or :SearchIsHprVar = 0 or :SearchIsHprVar is null) and (pj.is_portfolio=:SearchIsPortfolioVar or :SearchIsPortfolioVar = 0 or :SearchIsPortfolioVar is null) and (pj.area_code=:SearchAreaCodeVar or :SearchAreaCodeVar is null) and (pj.sbe_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchSbeCodeVar))) or :SearchSbeCodeVar is null) and (pj.ta_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchProjectTaCodeVar))) or :SearchProjectTaCodeVar is null) and (case when pj.program_id='RBIN' then 'deleted' when pj.is_active=1 then 'active' else 'inactive' end =:SearchStatusVar or :SearchStatusVar is null) and (instr(lower(pj.name||','||pj.previous_names),lower(:SearchProjectNameVar)) >0 or :SearchProjectNameVar is null) and (instr(lower(pj.code),lower(:SearchProjectCodeVar))>0 or :SearchProjectCodeVar is null) and pj.area_code in ('PRE-POT','POST-POT') and (instr(lower(bn.name),lower(:SearchProjectBayCodeVar)) >0 or :SearchProjectBayCodeVar is null) and (exists (select 1 from study_data_vw sd where sd.timeline_type_code in ('CUR','RAW') and sd.project_id=pj.id and instr(lower(sd.study_id),lower(:SearchStudyCodeVar))>0) or :SearchStudyCodeVar is null) ) ) and (exists (select 1 from team_member tm join employee emp on emp.code=tm.employee_code where tm.program_id=pg.id and instr(lower(emp.forename||' '||emp.surname),lower(:SearchEmployeeNameVar))>0) or :SearchEmployeeNameVar is null)
-- end Search filter Dev VC or -- begin Search filter for PrdMnt VC :SearchVcName='PrdMnt' and exists (select 1 from project pj left join ( select name, code from bay_number ) bn on bn.code = pj.bay_code where pj.program_id=pg.id and pj.area_code ='PRD-MNT' and (case when pj.program_id='RBIN' then 'deleted' when pj.is_active=1 then 'active' else 'inactive' end =:SearchStatusMnt or :SearchStatusMnt is null) and (instr(lower(pj.name||','||pj.previous_names),lower(:SearchProjectNameMnt)) >0 or :SearchProjectNameMnt is null) and (instr(lower(pj.code),lower(:SearchProjectCodeMnt))>0 or :SearchProjectCodeMnt is null) and (instr(lower(bn.name),lower(:SearchProjectBayCodeMnt)) >0 or :SearchProjectBayCodeMnt is null) ) -- end Search filter PrdMnt VC
or -- begin Search filter for LatestEstimatesDev VC :SearchVcName='LatestEstimatesDev' and exists (select 1 from project pj left join (select project_id, min(milestone_date) poc_date from milestone_vw where milestone_code='PoC' and timeline_type_code='CUR' group by project_id) milestone_poc on milestone_poc.project_id=pj.id where pj.program_id=pg.id and pj.area_code in ('PRE-POT','POST-POT') and pj.is_active=1 and (select 1 from timeline tm where tm.project_id=pj.id and tm.type_code='CUR')=1 and (instr(lower(pj.name||','||pj.previous_names),lower(:SearchProjectNameVar)) >0 or :SearchProjectNameVar is null) and (instr(lower(pj.code),lower(:SearchProjectCodeVar))>0 or :SearchProjectCodeVar is null) and (pj.state_code = :SearchProjectStateVar or :SearchProjectStateVar is null) and (milestone_poc.poc_date >= :SearchProjectPocDateFromVar or :SearchProjectPocDateFromVar is null) and (milestone_poc.poc_date <= :SearchProjectPocDateToVar or :SearchProjectPocDateToVar is null) and (pj.is_hpr=:SearchIsHprVar or :SearchIsHprVar = 0 or :SearchIsHprVar is null) and (pj.is_portfolio=:SearchIsPortfolioVar or :SearchIsPortfolioVar = 0 or :SearchIsPortfolioVar is null) and (pj.area_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchAreaCodeVar))) or :SearchAreaCodeVar is null) and (pj.sbe_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchSbeCodeVar))) or :SearchSbeCodeVar is null) and (pj.development_phase_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchProjectDevPhaseVar))) or :SearchProjectDevPhaseVar is null) and (pj.ta_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchProjectBUCodeVar))) or :SearchProjectBUCodeVar is null) and pj.id not in (select leprv.project_id from latest_estimates_project_vw leprv where leprv.tag_id=:CurrentLeTagIdVar) ) -- end Search filter LatestEstimatesDev VC
or -- begin Search filter for LatestEstimatesPrdMnt VC :SearchVcName='LatestEstimatesPrdMnt' and exists (select 1 from project pj where pj.program_id=pg.id and pj.area_code = 'PRD-MNT' and pj.is_active=1 and (select 1 from timeline tm where tm.project_id=pj.id and tm.type_code='CUR')=1 and (instr(lower(pj.name||','||pj.previous_names),lower(:SearchProjectNameMnt)) >0 or :SearchProjectNameMnt is null) and (instr(lower(pj.code),lower(:SearchProjectCodeMnt))>0 or :SearchProjectCodeMnt is null) and (pj.state_code = :SearchProjectStateMntVar or :SearchProjectStateMntVar is null) and (pj.sbe_code=:SearchSbeCodeVar or :SearchSbeCodeVar is null) and pj.id not in (select leprv.project_id from latest_estimates_project_vw leprv where leprv.tag_id=:CurrentLeTagIdVar) ) -- end Search filter LatestEstimatesPrdMnt VC
or -- begin Search filter for LtcDev VC :SearchVcName='LtcDev' and exists (select 1 from project pj left join (select project_id, min(milestone_date) poc_date from milestone_vw where milestone_code='PoC' and timeline_type_code='CUR' group by project_id) milestone_poc on milestone_poc.project_id=pj.id where pj.program_id=pg.id and pj.program_id <> 'RBIN' and pj.area_code in ('PRE-POT','POST-POT') and (pj.is_active=:SearchProjectIsActiveVar or :SearchProjectIsActiveVar is null) and (select 1 from timeline tm where tm.project_id=pj.id and tm.type_code='RAW')=1 and (instr(lower(pj.name||','||pj.previous_names),lower(:SearchProjectNameVar)) >0 or :SearchProjectNameVar is null) and (instr(lower(pj.code),lower(:SearchProjectCodeVar))>0 or :SearchProjectCodeVar is null) and (pj.state_code = :SearchProjectStateVar or :SearchProjectStateVar is null) and (pj.is_portfolio=:SearchIsPortfolioVar or :SearchIsPortfolioVar = 0 or :SearchIsPortfolioVar is null) and (pj.area_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchAreaCodeVar))) or :SearchAreaCodeVar is null) and (pj.sbe_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchSbeCodeVar))) or :SearchSbeCodeVar is null) and (pj.development_phase_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchProjectDevPhaseVar))) or :SearchProjectDevPhaseVar is null) and (pj.ta_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:SearchProjectBUCodeVar))) or :SearchProjectBUCodeVar is null) and pj.id not in (select leprv.project_id from ltc_project_vw leprv where leprv.tag_id=:CurrentLtcTagIdVar union all select leprv.project_id from ltc_project_vw leprv where leprv.status_code='RUN') ) -- end Search filter LtcDev VC
or -- begin Search filter for LtcPrdMnt VC :SearchVcName='LtcPrdMnt' and exists (select 1 from project pj where pj.program_id=pg.id and pj.program_id <> 'RBIN' and pj.area_code = 'PRD-MNT' and (pj.is_active=:SearchProjectIsActiveVar or :SearchProjectIsActiveVar is null) and (select 1 from timeline tm where tm.project_id=pj.id and tm.type_code='RAW')=1 and (instr(lower(pj.name||','||pj.previous_names),lower(:SearchProjectNameMnt)) >0 or :SearchProjectNameMnt is null) and (instr(lower(pj.code),lower(:SearchProjectCodeMnt))>0 or :SearchProjectCodeMnt is null) and (pj.state_code = :SearchProjectStateMntVar or :SearchProjectStateMntVar is null) and (pj.sbe_code=:SearchSbeCodeVar or :SearchSbeCodeVar is null) and pj.id not in (select leprv.project_id from ltc_project_vw leprv where leprv.tag_id=:CurrentLtcTagIdVar union all select leprv.project_id from ltc_project_vw leprv where leprv.status_code='RUN') ) -- end Search filter LtcPrdMnt VC
or :SearchVcName is null or :SearchVcName in ('D2Prj','D3Tr','Rs','Lg','Lo','Co','Unt','D1', 'SAMD') ) -- Application role filter and ( exists (select 1 from project prj where prj.program_id=pg.id and (prj.area_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:AllowedProjectTypes))) or prj.area_code is null and :RoleTypify='true')) or :SearchProgramIsEmptyVar=1 and :AllowedProjectTypes is not null or (exists (select 1 from project prj where prj.program_id=pg.id and prj.area_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:AllowedAssignedProjectTypes)))) or :SearchProgramIsEmptyVar=1 and :AllowedAssignedProjectTypes is not null ) and exists(select 1 from user_role url where UPPER(url.user_id)=UPPER(:UserNameVar) and url.program_id=pg.id) )
-- Fake bind variable instances and nvl(:UserNameVar,1)=nvl(:UserNameVar,1) and nvl(:RoleTypify,1)=nvl(:RoleTypify,1) Order by upper(Name)
